snippet.title: KAKU: Ancient Seal World Premiere Trailer (PC and PS5 & PS4)
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! And learn more:https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/KAKU_Ancient_Seal/

·Follow KAKU: Ancient Seal on twitter:https://twitter.com/KakuAncientSeal
·Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/t2HNE6E
·Like KAKU: Ancient Seal on Facebook:https://www.facebook.com/gaming/KakuAncientSealGameOfficial

KAKU: Ancient Seal is an  open-world action-adventure fantasy game that lets players navigate their own path through a mysterious continent full of strange creatures, ancient ruins, and unique tribes. Play Kaku an young child, who’s tasked with going on a journey across a sprawling continent.
